{"word":"G5143 - τρέχω - tréchō - trekh'-o - Have course","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">τρέχω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">tréchō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">trekh'-o</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Have course</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - ஒடு, பரப்பு"},{"paragraph":"to run"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>Apparently a primary verb (properly <b>&#x03B8;&#x03C1;&#x03B5;&#x0301;&#x03C7;&#x03C9;</b> <b>threcho&#x0304;</b>; compare <a href=\"#/G2359 - θρίξ - thríx - threeks/2359\">G2359</a>); which uses <b>&#x03B4;&#x03C1;&#x03B5;&#x0301;&#x03BC;&#x03C9;</b> <b>dremo&#x0304;</b>, <i>drem'-o</i> (the base of <a href=\"#/G1408 - δρόμος - drómos - drom'-os/1408\">G1408</a>) as an alternate in certain tenses; to <i>run</i> or <i>walk hastily</i> (literally or figuratively): - have course, run.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G1408/1408\">G1408</a>, <a href=\"#/G4274/4274\">G4274</a>, <a href=\"#/G5143/5143\">G5143</a>"}]}